descriptionViews.controlFunctionString:
  // A paper with no markers represents a 1x tile or a -1x tile 
  // and not 0x. We need to add or minus 1, and 
  // for the case of 1x not voice the coefficient. 
  // I think it is ok to voice -1x rather than -x.
if (Math.floor(NumberXCoefficient_D) === 0) {
    if (BooleanNegativeForX_D) {
        return 'minus x';
